    <description>This flow triggers when a piece of v1/2 fulfillment is moved to complete. It finds all of the other pieces of fulfillment (v1, 2 and 3) related to that advice, then sets a Flag to true. For each piece of fulfillment found, it checks if it is complete. If it&#39;s not, it sets the flag to false. At the end, if the flag is still true, the advice is moved to complete.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <interviewLabel>Move advice to complete once all fulfilment complete {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
